blog.name: kingdomofkitten
blog.title: Jacob A.K.A. KingdomOfKitten
blog.description:
I write sometimes. I think that says a lot about my career choices.

My Twitter: https://twitter.com/KingdomOfKitten

My Letterboxd: https://letterboxd.com/kingdomofkitten/

body:
AggretZooStars

*At the prestigious Cherryton School…*

Judy: Do they still do job presentations in this day and age? Let alone in high school?

Nick: Hey, Carrots, I don’t question the assignments given, I just do them.

Haida: Especially not one like this! Hehe…considering we get a raise if we do it.

Retsuko: Well, hey, cops, accountants, perfect jobs for adolescents to take on, right?

Nick: Well, actually, they seem like perfect jobs for adolescents to rebel agai-*bumps into someone* Yikes! Sorry about that, bro! Didn’t me-*sees the person, a quite large wolf*….whoa. O_O

Legosi: Oh. Uh, sorry. I didn’t see you there.

Judy: Um, t-that’s okay! He can be a little clumsy at times! Hehe…are, um, are you coming to the job presentation later today?

Legosi: Oh, that thing? I think we have t-

*suddenly, another rabbit, in high school attire, runs in*

Haru: Hi, Legosi!

Legosi: H-Haru! *blushes a little* What’s up?

Haru: Not much! Just trying to get to cl-*sees the other four* ….uh.

Judy: …what the….

Retsuko: ……I have never felt so weirdly out of place before in my life.

Legosi: ….well, um, yeah, er…she’s Haru, I’m Legosi.

Haru: We’re kinda pals.

Legosi: Yeah…pals.

Judy: …well, I am Judy Hopps, Zootopia police officer. This is my partner, and husband, Nick Wilde.

Nick: S’up.

Retsuko: And I’m Retsuko, I work at…actually, the name of the company escapes me at the moment, and this is my fiancée, Haida.

Haida: Hello.

Haru: …husband? Fiancée?

Judy: …yeah?

Legosi: ….you guys? Seriously?

Haida: Yeah? Is something the matter?

Haru: Well, no! It’s just…there’s a weird taboo about…you know, predators and prey around here.

Judy: Oh…well, I mean, there was a little in our city, didn’t stop us from getting married.

Retsuko: Hell, we didn’t even have any taboo where we live, we just kinda got together.

Haida: Well, granted, there was a little, due to the fact we’re co-workers.

Retsuko: Well, yeah. That, and it took a little bit for me to really love you like I do now.

Legosi: …it did?

Haida: Oh, yeah, I was kinda crushing on her hard, but we kinda started small. But now we’re getting married, and we have a kid, so, hehe! I guess it all worked out!

Haru: I…guess so.

*everyone has gone completely silent*

Nick: ….well! Would you look at the time, we gotta get ready!

Judy: …we do? Isn’t the presentation in a few hou-*sees Nick gesturing them, essentially, “let’s get the fuck out of here!”* oh! Uh, yeah! C’mon, guys!

Retsuko: Uh, okay! Bye, you two!

Haida: It was nice meeting you! *the four run off, leaving Legosi and Haru alone*

Legosi: …uh…

Haru: …I…need to go process…everything I just saw. *runs off*

Legosi: …there might still be hope yet. *walks away*

Everyone’s minds (except for Retsuko): WHAT THE FUCK JUST HAPPENED?!

Retsuko’s mind: Rabbit, rabbit, red panda….man, I stick out like a sore thumb!


So, I don’t know how many people have heard of Beastars, but I had gone through a bit of a binge session of it last year. I had just gotten reminded of it just a few days ago, and it essentially fueled this little goofy thing. I wish I could explain more my thought process behind it, but the only real thing I had to work off of was, “Nick, Haida, and Lugosi are tall-ish predators, and Judy, Retsuko, and Haru are small, cute, prey.” Real in-depth character studies, eh?


Follow me on Twitter, if you want: https://twitter.com/KingdomOfKitten

Follow me on Letterboxd, if you want: https://boxd.it/a0uL

Buy me a coffee, if you want: http://ko-fi.com/kingdomofkitten

summary:
Hey if yall take screenshots from a show and make icons 

 Dont make ppl credit you 

 THATS LIKE NEW LEVELS OF FUCKING WEIRD...
body:
Hey if yall take screenshots from a show and make icons

Dont make ppl credit you

THATS LIKE NEW LEVELS OF FUCKING WEIRD AND STUPID. You can disagree with me all you want but you didnt make the art in the show and anyone could do what you did so maybe get over yourself???

Sorry I dont mean to sound rly aggressive but it’s just rly rly aggervating to see people get famous for something stupid like that when they didnt even add anything. And I dont mean like pride flag stuff

that’s fine!

But when you go out of your way to take work from the show and make people credit YOU

That’s just plain odd and you dont deserve any credit tbh
